    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Dec 20, 2016</title>
      <link>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-20/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Dec 2016 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//cloudfeed.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2016-12-20/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Investments In Security Operations Centers Are Paying Off, Study Finds&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Another finding shows active threat-hunting as an increasingly useful mechanism for finding and stopping cyberthreats before systems become &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/partner-perspectives/intel/investments-in-security-operations-centers-are-paying-off-study-finds/a/d-id/1327750&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/partner-perspectives/intel/investments-in-security-operations-centers-are-paying-off-study-finds/a/d-id/1327750&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Global Application Performance Management (APM) Industry&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;II-33 SMBs Leverage APM SaaS to Enhance Competitiveness II-34 Log Management: A High Growth Area for APM Market II-35 Application Design &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/global-application-performance-management-apm-industry-300381607.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/global-application-performance-management-apm-industry-300381607.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Infographic: Changing Threat Landscape and Windows 10 Security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Notably, the last couple of years have seen some of the largest data breaches ever. Microsoft has been very particular about users&amp;rsquo; security, and it has &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.thewindowsclub.com/infographic-windows-10-security&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.thewindowsclub.com/infographic-windows-10-security&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Nigerian Hacker Breaches LA County, Data of 756000 Individuals Exposed&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No less than 108 employees of the Los Angeles County fell for a phishing attack that eventually exposed the details of no less than 756,000 &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://news.softpedia.com/news/nigerian-hacker-breaches-la-county-data-of-756-000-individuals-exposed-511126.shtml&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://news.softpedia.com/news/nigerian-hacker-breaches-la-county-data-of-756-000-individuals-exposed-511126.shtml&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Ultimate Software gets data privacy certification&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the recent spate of data breaches across the globe, there is increasing concern from companies about the security of their data in the cloud.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.enterprisetimes.co.uk/2016/12/20/ultimate-software-gets-data-privacy-certification/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.enterprisetimes.co.uk/2016/12/20/ultimate-software-gets-data-privacy-certification/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Big Data: The 6th &amp;lsquo;V&amp;rsquo; Everyone Should Know About&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s partly because it&amp;rsquo;s new but it&amp;rsquo;s also because everyone&amp;rsquo;s seen stories in the press about data breaches, and most people have experienced their &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.forbes.com/sites/bernardmarr/2016/12/20/big-data-the-6th-v-everyone-should-know-about/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.forbes.com/sites/bernardmarr/2016/12/20/big-data-the-6th-v-everyone-should-know-about/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Using Threat Analysis In the Security Operations Center&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But as threat intelligence becomes more sophisticated and threat hunting becomes a more common tool in the security department, the nature of &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://webinar.darkreading.com/2698?keycode=SBX&amp;cid=smartbox_techweb_webcast_8.500000686&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://webinar.darkreading.com/2698?keycode=SBX&amp;cid=smartbox_techweb_webcast_8.500000686&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Protecting your firms data safety in a world of digital disruption&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; draft of new mandatory data breach notification laws that will form part of the Privacy Amendment (Notification of Serious Data Breaches) Bill 2015.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.lawyersweekly.com.au/partner-features/20272-protecting-your-firms-data-safety-in-a-world-of-digital-disruption&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.lawyersweekly.com.au/partner-features/20272-protecting-your-firms-data-safety-in-a-world-of-digital-disruption&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;12 cybersecurity trends &amp;amp; predictions for 2017&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The end of signature detection Whether we call this next generation AV or end point protection or endpoint detection and response, clearly we are &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itproportal.com/features/12-cybersecurity-trends-predictions-for-2017/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itproportal.com/features/12-cybersecurity-trends-predictions-for-2017/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Flashback 2016: Tech Hits and Misses This Year&lt;/h3&gt;
